
Controlling Measurement Equipment with Python and SCPI via VXI-11 and USBTMC
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Introduction to controlling test and measurement equipment from Python on Linux
via VXI-11 and USBTMC. Equipment used in the presentation: RIGOL DG1022 and
RIGOL DS2072. Examples include sampling and decoding a single frame from a PAL
video signal.

Watch on Youtube:
http://youtu.be/a0VKY9klUjQ

Discuss on Redit:
http://redd.it/1o5f8h

Files on GitHub:
